wiki.summary: On “I Can Show You,” Uzi uses his classic braggadocious style to talk about how girls will do anything to get money from him, and that he would never chase after a girl, only money. He continues to boast about his great taste in fashion and how much money he has with a water-like flow on the song, over a hypnotic melody from Working On Dying group member Oogie Mane. “I Can Show You” debuted at #66 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart for the chart week of March 28, 2020. Read more on Last.fm.
